 אורתוגונלים:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda_{2}\left\langle u,v\right\rangle =\left\langle Au,v\right\rangle =\left\langle A^{t}u,v\right\rangle =\left\langle u,Av\right\rangle =\left\langle u,\lambda v\right\rangle =\lambda_{1}\left\langle u,v\right\rangle 
\]

\end_inset


